[SN]TITLE[SN]
Elite League play-off semi-final: Coventry Blaze 6-2 Cardiff Devils

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Chris Bruton's treble helped Coventry Blaze into Sunday's Elite League final as the defending play-off champions eased to victory over Cardiff Devils.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Canadian forward helped stun the regular season runners-up as Coventry raced into a 4-0 first-period lead.
Brett Robinson, Cale Tanaka and Josh Godfrey also scored for Blaze as they set up a final against Nottingham Panthers or Fife Flyers.
Joey Haddad and Gleason Fournier added late consolations goals for Cardiff.
